09:10.015 --> 09:11.017
- UH-OH.

09:11.019 --> 09:14.015
- [GRUNTING]

09:16.014 --> 09:20.012
[SCREAMING]

09:21.027 --> 09:23.009
- GIRLS!

09:23.011 --> 09:24.028
GIRLS! OH, THANK GOODNESS.

09:25.000 --> 09:26.019
