FOR YOU.

09:26.021 --> 09:28.014
WHY ARE YOU LAYING ON THE GROUND
LIKE THAT?

09:28.016 --> 09:30.001
WHAT HAPPENED TO MY BABIES?

09:30.003 --> 09:32.016
- WOOH--SUNBURNS.

09:32.018 --> 09:33.025
- SUNBURNS?

09:33.027 --> 09:36.015
OH, YEAH. HA HA HA!

09:36.017 --> 09:37.027
- IT'S NOT FUNNY.

09:37.029 --> 09:40.026
- AND YOU THOUGHT SUNSCREEN
WOULD MAKE YOU LOOK LIKE DORKS.

09:40.028 --> 09:42.014
HA HA HA!

09:42.016 --> 09:44.019
- OK, WE GET IT.

09:44.021 --> 09:46.004
WE'RE SORRY.

09:46.006 --> 09:48.017
- PLEASE HELP US, PROFESSOR.

09:48.019 --> 09:49.029
- WELL, LUCKY FOR YOU,

09:50.001 --> 09:53.003
