YOU SEE, WE KNEW THAT PEOPLE
WOULD BE TOO COOL FOR SUNSCREEN

09:56.009 --> 09:57.027
WHEN WE INVENTED IT.

09:57.029 --> 10:01.001
SO, INSTEAD OF CONNING
STUPID PEOPLE OUT OF THEIR MONEY

