- HEY! NOT BAD.

10:36.007 --> 10:38.015
- NOT BAD AT ALL.

10:38.017 --> 10:40.006
- THIS STUFF REALLY WORKS.

10:40.008 --> 10:41.020
- I FEEL TINGLY.

10:41.022 --> 10:43.019
- WHAT--WHAT'S HAPPENING?

10:45.003 --> 10:46.017
