11:13.005 --> 11:15.005
- WE'VE GOT A BETTER IDEA.

11:17.016 --> 11:20.022
- YOU KNOW,
THEY DID GIVE US SUNSCREEN.

11:20.024 --> 11:22.026
- SUNSCREEN IS FOR NERDS!

11:24.019 --> 11:26.027
- AND SO ONCE AGAIN,
THE DAY IS SAVED,

11:26.029 --> 11:29.007
THANKS TO...THE PROFESSOR!

11:29.009 --> 11:31.013
- HEY! WHO WANTS MY AUTOGRAPH?

11:31.015 --> 11:33.017
- DON'T PUSH YOUR LUCK, NERD.

11:49.006 --> 11:51.005
- THE CITY OF TOWNSVILLE:

11:51.007 --> 11:53.001
