16:46.012 --> 16:50.020
[LAUGHING]

16:52.020 --> 16:56.001
CONGRATULATE ME,
SORROWPUFF GIRL.

16:56.003 --> 17:01.005
I'VE LOST THIS CONTEST TO YOU
FOR 6 YEARS RUNNING.

17:01.007 --> 17:05.016
BUT NOW, THANKS TO THE WONDERS
OF TECHNOLOGY,

17:05.018 --> 17:08.020
I'M TOWNSVILLE'S...

17:08.022 --> 17:11.020
HAPPIEST CITIZEN!

17:13.002 --> 17:18.000
[LAUGHING]

17:23.002 --> 17:24.011
- WHOO! WHOO!

17:24.013 --> 17:25.023
[LAUGHING]

17:26.022 --> 17:29.009
- WHAT DO WE DO NOW,
PROFESSOR?

17:29.011 --> 17:33.012
- GIRLS, THE ONLY KNOWN CURE
FOR THE EFFECTS OF THE MISERAY

17:33.014 --> 17:36.003
IS SOMETHING MORE CONTAGIOUS
THAN SADNESS,

17:36.005 --> 17:39.010
AND THAT'S A SENSE OF HUMOR.

17:39.012 --> 17:40.029
- YOU MEAN...

17:41.001 --> 17:43.006
- BEING FUNNY?

17:43.008 --> 17:46.026
- YES. MAKE JUST
ONE PERSON HERE LAUGH--

17:46.028 --> 17:48.009
JUST ONE, MIND YOU--

17:48.011 --> 17:51.025
AND THE ENTIRE TOWN WILL...

17:51.027 --> 17:53.015
FOLLOW!

17:53.017 --> 17:56.026
[WAILING]

17:57.018 --> 17:59.023
- BUT, PROFESSOR...

17:59.025 --> 18:03.019
- HOW CAN WE MAKE
ANYONE LAUGH...

18:03.021 --> 18:05.023
- WHEN WE'RE SO...

18:05.025 --> 18:07.028
- UNHAPPY?

18:08.000 --> 18:10.022
[WAILING]

18:10.024 --> 18:12.015
- CRYING IS EASY, GIRLS.

18:12.017 --> 18:14.022
COMEDY IS HARD.

18:14.024 --> 18:17.010
NOW GO UP THERE
AND KNOCK 'EM OUT.

18:20.027 --> 18:23.012
- IS THIS THING ON?

18:23.014 --> 18:26.013
GOOD EVENING,
LADIES AND GERMS.

18:27.017 --> 18:30.005
- WE JUST FLEW IN
FROM LAS VEGAS...

18:30.007 --> 18:32.018
- BECAUSE WE CAN.

18:32.020 --> 18:35.009
[WAILS]

18:35.011 --> 18:38.005
[CROWD WAILING]

18:41.018 --> 18:44.020
ROUGH CROWD.

18:44.022 --> 18:47.015
- STEP ON IT, BECAUSE ACCORDING
TO MY CALCULATIONS,

18:47.017 --> 18:51.009
THE ENTIRE TOWN WILL BE FLOODED
WITH TEARS IN 10 MINUTES!

18:51.024 --> 18:54.015
[WAILING]

18:55.014 --> 18:57.014
MAKE THAT 5 MINUTES.

18:57.016 --> 18:59.023
- [SCREAMING]

18:59.025 --> 19:03.013
- AH, THE LOVELY SOUND
OF OTHER PEOPLE CRYING.

19:03.015 --> 19:05.015
IT'S SO REFRESHING.

19:05.017 --> 19:09.008
YOU KNOW, TOWNSVILLE
IS SUCH A SILLY NAME.

19:09.010 --> 19:11.020
