AND HAS LOTS OF APPEAL?

19:36.009 --> 19:38.010
A BANANA!

19:43.015 --> 19:45.019
- SEE?

19:45.021 --> 19:48.001
A PEEL. GET IT?

19:50.011 --> 19:52.015
I GIVE UP!

19:52.017 --> 19:54.022
[WAILS]

19:57.004 --> 19:59.019
- IT WAS NICE KNOWING YOU,
FROWNSVILLE.

19:59.021 --> 20:02.024
I THINK I'LL GO HOME
AND POLISH MY TROPHY NOW.

20:02.026 --> 20:04.026
♪ GOOD-BYE ♪

20:28.021 --> 20:29.029
